Trains.io 3D Game Offline Version (Only 1MB)

INTRODUCTION
Trains.io 3D is slithering train game in 3d world. Become the grand trainin game by eating others and grow longer. Collect screws and toolboks to grow faster!

HOW TO INSTALL?
1. Click "Add to Chrome" to install the extension
2. Pin the Trains.io 3D extension icon to the Chrome toolbar
3. Click the Trains.io 3D icon on the Chrome toolbar, the Trains.io 3D popup will open. 
That's all you need to do! Have fun!

HOW TO PLAY?
Click to boost on desktop. Double tap to boost on mobile.
